905
01:30:45,087 --> 01:30:46,631
Go faster dad, go faster.

906
01:30:46,965 --> 01:30:49,343
Hunter, what color...
the car was red, right?

907
01:30:49,676 --> 01:30:52,263
Yeah, a little red Chevy.

908
01:30:57,144 --> 01:30:59,522
