914
01:31:13,455 --> 01:31:16,583
- The right one!
- Alright, settle down, I see it.

915
01:31:20,880 --> 01:31:23,841
See if it's her. Can you tell?

916
01:31:25,594 --> 01:31:27,430
I can't tell.

917
01:31:27,722 --> 01:31:29,808
